
==============================================================================
==============================================================================
=================== [ Ionis Users Informations PHP Class ] ===================
==============================================================================

A PHP Class to get informations about students in Ionis group :
Isbp, Epitech, Etna, Ipsa, Epita, e-art, Web@cademie, ...


============================== [ Requirement ] ===============================

- PHP >= 5.3
- libssh2-php

================================= [ Usage ] ==================================

1) Initialisation

   $ionis = new IonisInfo($login, $pass);
   where $login is your ionis (exampl_e) and $pass is your unix password.


2) Functions

- Get a login from the uid :
     $ionis->getLoginFromUid($uid)

- Get uid, name, group, school, promo, city from the login :
    $ionis->getUid($login);
    $ionis->getName($login);
    $ionis->getGroup($login);
    $ionis->getSchool($login);
    $ionis->getPromo($login);
    $ionis->getCity($login);

- Get Report Url :
    $ionis->getReportUrl($login);

- Get photos :
    $ionis->getPhotoUrl($login);
    get the url from the intra.
    $ionis->copyPhoto($login, $directory);
    copy the photo locally.

- Get .plan file :
    $ionis->getPlan($plan);
    copy the .plan public file (afs) locally and return its content.

- Check the PPP password :
    $ionis->checkPass($login, $pass);
    return true if the password match for the login, false otherwise.

- Update informations files
    $ionis->updateFiles();
    update the informations files. Good idea to put it in a crontab.


3) Example

   See the example.php file.


==============================================================================
==============================================================================
============================= [ MySQL Version ] ==============================
==============================================================================

This version keep informations in a MySQL database. It's faster.

============================== [ Requirement ] ===============================

MySQL

CREATE TABLE `your_database`.`ionisusersinformations`
  (
    `id` INT UNSIGNED NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY ,
    `login` VARCHAR( 128 ) NOT NULL ,
    `uid` INT NOT NULL ,
    `promo` INT NOT NULL ,
    `pass` VARCHAR( 255 ) NOT NULL ,
    `school` VARCHAR( 255 ) NOT NULL ,
    `groupe` VARCHAR( 255 ) NOT NULL ,
    `name` VARCHAR( 255 ) NOT NULL ,
    `city` VARCHAR( 128 ) NOT NULL ,
    UNIQUE
      (
        `login`
      )
  );

================================= [ Usage ] ==================================

1) Initialisation

   new IonisInfoSQL($mysql_login, $mysql_pass, $database_name, $ionis_login, $ionis_unix_pass);

2) Other informations

   See above.

3) Id

   - Get login from the id :
     $ionis->getLoginFromId($id)

   - Get the id from the login :
     $ionis->getId($login);


